[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0428","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0243","title":"Linux cfingerd 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux cfingerd（可配置的 Finger 服务守护进程）存在远程权限提升漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 Finger 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取目标系统 root 最高权限，完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版中运行的 cfingerd 服务，攻击者无需任何认证即可远程发起攻击，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0243"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.250","remediation":"立即停止并卸载 cfingerd 服务（`systemctl stop cfingerd && apt-get remove cfingerd` 或 `yum remove cfingerd`）。cfingerd 已在 2000 年代初停止维护，不存在补丁修复。建议在 iptables 或防火墙中封禁 TCP 端口 79，同时禁用 finger 协议。改用现代认证机制（如 LDAP/SSSD）替代 finger 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.geocrawler.com/archives/3/92/1996/9/0/2217716/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0243","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0243.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_format_bug.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe9025