-1999-0268","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0268.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0268.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pmvg-g2g6-mpp9/GHSA-pmvg-g2g6-mpp9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0268.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82098/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0454.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0462","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0462.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0276","title":"Hughes Technologies mSQL 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"mSQL（Mini SQL）2.0.1 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标服务的 1114 端口发送特制的畸型数据包，触发栈缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖返回地址，实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 mSQL 2.0.1 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0276"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.350","remediation":"立即将 mSQL 升级至 v2.0.1 以上版本（如 2.0.2 或更高），该版本修复了 wprint 函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。由于 mSQL 已停止维护多年，强烈建议迁移至受支持的数据库产品，如 MariaDB 或 PostgreSQL。在无法迁移前，应通过在防火墙上限制对 mSQL 默认端口（1114/TCP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 IP 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0276","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-19